title: The One Where Lala Goes Straight Off Insta & Down In The DMs
description:
Straight off the Insta & outta the DMS, it’s ask Lala anything with an assist and extra commentary from Jessica. They talk about toxic friendships, cutting people loose, what it really means to be a bitch, anxiety & depression, and the real truth about how motherhood (and in Jessica’s case, pet parenthood) changes lives. Lala also spills a drop of tea or two on season 10 of Vanderpump Rules and where she stands when it comes to Stassi Schroeder and Brittany Cartwright.
